  - key: pass.asceta.desc
    translations:
    - Quanto mais baixo o HP, maior o dano causado.
    - The lower your HP, the higher your damage.
    - "Cuanto menor es tu HP, mayor es tu da\xF1o."
    - "Je niedriger dein HP, desto h\xF6her dein Schaden."
    - "Plus votre HP est bas, plus vos d\xE9g\xE2ts sont \xE9lev\xE9s."
    - "Minore \xE8 il tuo HP, maggiore \xE8 il danno."
    - "\u0427\u0435\u043C \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044C\u0448\u0435 HP, \u0442\u0435\u043C
      \u0432\u044B\u0448\u0435 \u0443\u0440\u043E\u043D."
    - "Im mniejsze HP, tym wi\u0119ksze obra\u017Cenia."
    - "HP ne kadar d\xFC\u015F\xFCkse, hasar o kadar y\xFCksek."
    - "HP\u8D8A\u4F4E\uFF0C\u9020\u6210\u7684\u4F24\u5BB3\u8D8A\u9AD8\u3002"
    - "HP\u304C\u4F4E\u3044\u307B\u3069\u3001\u4E0E\u3048\u308B\u30C0\u30E1\u30FC\u30B8\u304C\u5927\u304D\u304F\u306A\u308A\u307E\u3059\u3002"
    - "HP\uAC00 \uB099\uC744\uC218\uB85D \uAC00\uD558\uB294 \uD53C\uD574\uAC00 \uCEE4\uC9D1\uB2C8\uB2E4."
    - Hoe lager je HP, hoe hoger je schade.
    - Semakin rendah HP, semakin tinggi kerusakan yang diberikan.
