    - "\u5931\u8D25\uFF01"
    - "\u5931\u6557\uFF01"
    - "\uC2E4\uD328!"
    - MISLUKT!
    - GAGAL!
  - key: event.not_completed
    translations:
    - "Evento n\xE3o completado."
    - Event not completed.
    - Evento no completado.
    - Ereignis nicht abgeschlossen.
    - "\xC9v\xE9nement non termin\xE9."
    - Evento non completato.
    - "\u0421\u043E\u0431\u044B\u0442\u0438\u0435 \u043D\u0435 \u0437\u0430\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0448\u0435\u043D\u043E."
    - "Wydarzenie nieuko\u0144czone."
    - "Etkinlik tamamlanmad\u0131."
    - "\u4E8B\u4EF6\u672A\u5B8C\u6210\u3002"
    - "\u30A4\u30D9\u30F3\u30C8\u672A\u5B8C\u4E86\u3002"
    - "\uC774\uBCA4\uD2B8 \uBBF8\uC644\uB8CC."
    - Gebeurtenis niet voltooid.
    - Event tidak selesai.
  - key: event.reward.heal15
    translations:
    - +15% de vida recuperada!
    - +15% health recovered!
    - "\xA1+15% de vida recuperada!"
    - +15% Leben wiederhergestellt!
    - "+15% de vie r\xE9cup\xE9r\xE9e!"
    - +15% di vita recuperata!
    - "+15% \u0437\u0434\u043E\u0440\u043E\u0432\u044C\u044F \u0432\u043E\u0441\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043D\u043E\u0432\u043B\u0435\u043D\u043E!"
    - +15% odzyskanego zdrowia!
    - "+%15 can geri kazan\u0131ld\u0131!"
