    - "\uCCB4\uB825 15% \uD68C\uBCF5!"
    - +15% levenspunten herwonnen!
    - +15% HP dipulihkan!
  - key: event.reward.heal20
    translations:
    - +20% de vida recuperada!
    - +20% health recovered!
    - "\xA1+20% de vida recuperada!"
    - +20% Leben wiederhergestellt!
    - "+20% de vie r\xE9cup\xE9r\xE9e!"
    - +20% di vita recuperata!
    - "+20% \u0437\u0434\u043E\u0440\u043E\u0432\u044C\u044F \u0432\u043E\u0441\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043D\u043E\u0432\u043B\u0435\u043D\u043E!"
    - +20% odzyskanego zdrowia!
